---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Guides & Resources - Springfield Municipal Permit Portal</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background: #1a365d;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
        }
        header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        
        nav {
            background: #2c5282;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        nav a { color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
        nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        
        .breadcrumbs {
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        .breadcrumbs a { color: #2c5282; }
        
        main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
        
        h2 { color: #1a365d; margin-top: 0; }
        
        .guides-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .guide-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .guide-card .content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .guide-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
            color: #1a365d;
        }
        
        .guide-card p {
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        .guide-card a {
            color: #2c5282;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .guide-card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        
        .guide-card.suspended {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        
        .guide-card.suspended .badge {
            background: #e53e3e;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        footer {
            background: #1a365d;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Springfield Municipal Permit Portal</h1>
    </header>
    
    <nav>
        <a href="/l1/springfield/">Home</a>
        <a href="/l1/springfield/apply">Apply Online</a>
        <a href="/l1/springfield/search?id=12345">Permit Search</a>
        <a href="/l1/springfield/guides">Guides & Resources</a>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="breadcrumbs">
        <a href="/l1/springfield/">Home</a> &gt; Guides & Resources
    </div>
    
    <main>
        <h2>Permit Guides & Resources</h2>
        
        <div class="guides-grid">
            <div class="guide-card">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Building Permit Guide</h3>
                    <p>Everything you need to know about applying for a building permit, including required documents and fees.</p>
                    <a href="#">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="guide-card suspended">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Fence Permit <span class="badge">Suspended</span></h3>
                    <p>Requirements for installing or replacing fences, including height restrictions and property line guidelines.</p>
                    <a href="/l1/springfield/guides/fences">View Guide</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="guide-card">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Electrical Permit</h3>
                    <p>Guidelines for electrical work permits, including service upgrades and new construction requirements.</p>
                    <a href="#">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="guide-card">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Plumbing Permit</h3>
                    <p>Information on plumbing permits for new installations, repairs, and modifications.</p>
                    <a href="#">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="guide-card">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>HVAC Permit</h3>
                    <p>Requirements for heating, ventilation, and air conditioning system permits.</p>
                    <a href="#">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="guide-card">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Pool & Spa Permit</h3>
                    <p>Safety requirements and permit procedures for residential pools and spas.</p>
                    <a href="#">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 City of Springfield. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
